Class Employee

  • java.lang.Object
    • entities.Employee

  • public class Employee
extends java.lang.Object
    this class represents Employee object- it has variables that we need to save an employee details. we use this classe's instance in order to build the employee table for the use of Marketing rep when updating employee. every variable has its getters and setters, we use this class's constructor in "MarketingRepUpdateEmployeeC".
